title: 0-100 in less than a second. And I'm driving.
description:
AMZ Racing's "mythen" holds the world record for electric vehicle acceleration: 0-100km/h in 0.956 seconds. And they let me drive it. ■ AMZ: https://www.amzracing.ch/en https://www.instagram.com/amzracing/ ■ Their world record video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=88cVs5zZFTE

Main camera op: Juan Pablo Salazar
Additional cam op: Tobias Binder
Drone camera ops: Felix Kunz, Marco Odeermatt
